<!-- Definition ad effectiveness -->
'''白喉疫苗'''是一種用來對抗{{tsl|en|Corynebacterium diphtheriae|白喉桿菌|白喉桿菌}}的疫苗，而白喉桿菌正是[[白喉|白喉]]的致病原<ref name="urlMedlinePlus Medical Encyclopedia: Diphtheria immunization (vaccine)">{{cite web|url=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/MEDLINEPLUS/ency/article/002018.htm |title=MedlinePlus Medical Encyclopedia: Diphtheria immunization (vaccine) |work= |accessdate=2009-03-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090302121738/http://www.nlm.nih.gov/MEDLINEPLUS/ency/article/002018.htm |archivedate=March 2, 2009 }}</ref>。在1980年到2000年間，白喉疫苗的出現讓白喉患者的感染人數減少90%之多<ref name=WHO2006/>。前三劑施打的疫苗可提供約95%免疫力，其效力可達十年之久，並建議在十年後再追加施打一劑<ref name=WHO2006/>。 目前會讓出生六週的嬰孩接種疫苗並在接下來每四週追加施打一劑<ref name=WHO2006/>。

<!-- Safety -->
白喉疫苗非常安全<ref name=WHO2006/>。只有極少數的案例有嚴重的[[副作用|副作用]]<ref name=WHO2006/>。在施打部位可能伴隨有[[疼痛|疼痛]]感，在接種後幾週注射部位也可能有腫起的情形<ref name=CDC2012Pink>{{cite book|last1=Atkinson|first1=William|title=Diphtheria Epidemiology and Prevention of Vaccine-Preventable Diseases|date=May 2012|publisher=Public Health Foundation|isbn=9780983263135|pages=215–230|edition=12|url=http://www.cdc.gov/vaccines/pubs/pinkbook/dip.html|access-date=2016-09-17|archive-date=2013-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130720030015/http://www.cdc/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此疫苗對孕婦又或是免疫功能不全的患者都是相對安全的，並不需特別注意。

<!-- Usage -->
有許多混合疫苗被用來預防白喉<ref>{{cite web|author=Centre for Disease Control and Prevention|title=Diphtheria Vaccination|url=http://www.cdc.gov/vaccines/vpd-vac/diphtheria/default.htm#vacc|publisher=Department of Health and Human Services|accessdate=8 November 2011|archive-date=2011-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111102042325/http://www.cdc.gov/vaccines/vpd-vac/diphtheria/default.htm#vacc|dead-url=no}}</ref>；其中包括 [[破傷風疫苗|破傷風類毒素疫苗]]（又稱為 [[百白破疫苗|破傷風疫苗或DT疫苗]]）或是被稱為DPT的[[百白破疫苗|百日咳白喉破傷風三聯疫苗]]<ref name=WHO2006/>。自1974年起，世界衛生組織就廣泛的推廣這些疫苗的使用<ref name=WHO2006>{{cite journal|title=Diphtheria vaccine|journal=Wkly Epidemiol Rec|date=Jan 20, 2006|volume=81|issue=3|pages=24–32|pmid=16671240|url=http://www.who.int/wer/2006/wer8103.pdf|access-date=2016-09-17|archive-date=2015-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150606054559/http://www.who.int/wer/2006/wer8103.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，目前約有84%的世界人口已接種<ref>{{cite web|title=Diphtheria|url=http://www.who.int/immunization/monitoring_surveillance/burden/diphtheria/en/|website=who.int|accessdate=27 March 2015|date=3 September 2014|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402121723/http://www.who.int/immunization/monitoring_surveillance/burden/diphtheria/en/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此疫苗是經由[[肌肉注射|肌肉注射]]的方式給予<ref name=WHO2006/>，保存方式為冷藏而不是冷凍<ref name=CDC2012Pink/>。

<!-- Society and culture -->
白喉疫苗於1923年問世<ref>{{cite book|last1=Macera|first1=Caroline|title=Introduction to Epidemiology: Distribution and Determinants of Disease|date=2012|publisher=Nelson Education|isbn=9781285687148|page=251|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=U8FuCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA251|access-date=2016-09-17|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305040732/https://books.google.ca/books?id=U8FuCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA251|dead-url=no}}</ref>，為名列[[世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单|世界衛生組織基本藥物標準清單內的藥物]]，同時也是{{tsl|en|health system|基礎醫療系統|基礎醫療系統}}內的重要必須藥品<ref>{{cite web|title=WHO Model List of EssentialMedicines|url=http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/93142/1/EML_18_eng.pdf?ua=1|work=World Health Organization|accessdate=22 April 2014|date=October 2013|archive-date=2014-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140423005004/http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/93142/1/EML_18_eng.pdf?ua=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。混合有破傷風類毒素的白喉混合疫苗，在2014年的量販價格約介於0.12到0.99美元間<ref>{{cite web|title=Vaccine, Diphtheria-Tetanus|url=http://erc.msh.org/dmpguide/resultsdetail.cfm?language=english&code=DT00X&s_year=2014&year=2014&str=&desc=Vaccine%2C%20Diphtheria-Tetanus&pack=new&frm=VIAL&rte=INJ&class_code2=19%2E3%2E&supplement=&class_name=%2819%2E3%2E%29Vaccines%3Cbr%3E|website=International Drug Price Indicator Guide|accessdate=6 December 2015}}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，美國的售價則是低於25美元。<ref name=Ric2015>{{cite book|last1=Hamilton|first1=Richart|title=Tarascon Pocket Pharmacopoeia 2015 Deluxe Lab-Coat Edition|date=2015|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|isbn=9781284057560|page=313}}</ref>

